The '''Northern Frontier''' was the mountainous northern hemisphere of [[Sevarcos II]]. During the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], it was governed by [[Spice lord|Spice Lord]] [[Lady/Legends|Lady]] [[Trevael]] and relatively free of [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] presence.

